{"tid":39362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我要探索黑洞的奧秘，各位唔駛理我。","createTime":"2016-12-14T13:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T16:41:23.000Z","uid":60128,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3da84a4afd13539466700cc2a92e41cfbc19ea9","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:59:55.000Z","msg":"月黑風高，黑洞神祕。<br />\n雖然我怕黑，但癡線佬是一種孤高又神秘的生物，好奇心少不了。<br />\n看看在1小時零2分19秒裡面，我想說什麼就說什麼。<br />\n<br />\n原來，直接在黑洞發唔到post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n那唯有，不停在這裡自言自語。希望admin掉我落黑洞。"},{"pid":"e677a3308f1a79f2424d5df6fb2be59661f9f7c4","tid":39362,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:00:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc260f2c995df52dc641d37d9bd51d785d39ee2","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:01:27.000Z","msg":"如果天空要下雨，唯有愛人是個處。<br />\n有一日，總會有人和你分開。<br />\n但，在這之前，請你不要忘記我食左你隻豬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1feaf9ad543eec43fbee9f41daa56ed2aeb1fc1e","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:03:17.000Z","msg":"有些時候，你會想沉默。<br />\n有些時候，你會想發瘋。<br />\n有些時候，你會想做愛。<br />\n<br />\n但，屌你，想咁多做乜野，立刻去做啦屌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d592af9aee500edccfa42996f85bab594b75bc49","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:05:38.000Z","msg":"明明知道結果，但還是想去做。<br />\n可能會後悔，但唔做也是會後悔。<br />\n所以，你要明白，過程才是最重要，<br />\n因它會變成回憶，是其他人帶不走的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5ae2bacd629776b8eded4c3783192aa85923ad","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:07:50.000Z","msg":"沒有人可以對你一生一世的誠諾。<br />\n因誠諾只不過是口頭上說的，但好方面想，可能那一刻是真心的呢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645fda5c61f3b7d0f87d1efe56bd582ef57e2dff","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"人越大，朋友越多，真心越少。<br />\n做一個癡線佬係唔會理咁嘅野，佢只會理：<br />\n<br />\n今晚扑野夜唔夜呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da0127ee7f7bb2e96391ccb712e0fa94d725ae7","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:10:53.000Z","msg":"唉，唔想玩10連，但又入唔到黑洞，如何是好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e862145eeac4256457cb02ca1ad9dd318a9f730f","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:12:08.000Z","msg":"不過這post也好，起碼打錯字唔駛比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109ac708f5a4b8f1e83f7b7a6740474548cb329d","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:13:19.000Z","msg":"人生在世，癡線最架勢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e01063bfa34b1a487773c570b62e0bf2012264","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:15:06.000Z","msg":"你唔需要比人聰明，<br />\n你唔需要比人幽默，<br />\n你唔需要比人靚仔。<br />\n<br />\n那你需要什麼？<br />\n就是你要比人更有耐心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d84d80a308683dc0c11572494ef4eed09eeb66","tid":39362,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:16:13.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1203c9968d866af2f3c15da9e533f7980a960837","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:17:07.000Z","msg":"只要你夠恆心做一件事，<br />\n不管結局如何，最後勝利一定係你。<br />\n依種就係癡線佬自我打飛機大法，包你爽到射。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d7056136ce53437ba001e1f87e751ff308589c","tid":39362,"uid":65562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:18:30.000Z","msg":"威士忌留名#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#lm"},{"pid":"1dc17618442605c1ab2d2cd4737494d0ad246ebc","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:18:58.000Z","msg":"你不能得到全世界人歡心，總有人看你不順眼。<br />\n但細心一諗，其他人關你撚事咩，佢又唔係你條撚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375f7071fd7e290fdf99e096e6a1bb5d538ce1b3","tid":39362,"uid":23661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:20:13.000Z","msg":"痴線佬你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ab2efb2e4829cd7c169efc23957108a22dd39e","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:20:51.000Z","msg":"原來不停出post都幾累下，還有36分鐘28秒，可以出幾多野呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22dff80d0f9142ab36b5418076ce6e2fd8f25e1","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:21:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴線佬你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfb9d57fccf18dda45eec9a9f0fc8591400d944","tid":39362,"uid":23661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:23:12.000Z","msg":"會唔會繼續上次個故<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23495211b50c3e4707fc1160cab059e2fd268714","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:23:15.000Z","msg":"唔知點解，我好喜歡寫清楚時分秒和數目。<br />\n唯一解釋，可能我是癡線的。<br />\n也習慣了，這是一種個人風格，抄不了，改不來。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07702962b447a20d3eda3e0176ce0d77b207835","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:24:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會繼續上次個故<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我本來就唔識寫文，詞語貧窮。<br />\n還有，我唔識中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fa5c24ed8a9b8d9565d395036078fedcd247db","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:26:39.000Z","msg":"當你覺得萬事起頭難，10鳩幾樣野要一齊發生。<br />\n那，請先求其做一樣先。<br />\n逃避，永遠只得個想。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f4fe93af7748a4d36cc65859ed21bfc6b198cd","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:27:46.000Z","msg":"其實我好撚靚仔。<br />\n我份人唔講大話，一講就打個尿震。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e903a9c4575912f314632ac8df3733579fd3e9e2","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"今天的賓州有點喧囂。<br />\n我是的州心動，還是我的鳩想動。<br />\n我看不透...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383e4ec725fc412b1d42affa3c77cf9380342cdb","tid":39362,"uid":1701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0ff3d2be18dc80360dc66cfaf649f958b6a4e6","tid":39362,"uid":23661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:32:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會繼續上次個故<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我本來就唔識寫文，詞語貧窮。<br />\n還有，我唔識中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重諗住有痴線故事睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502923d7275b91d64fa85e06c6c90219cd9041df","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"男人無論幾多歲都是專一和貪心的。<br />\n幾多歲都希望找個大波有錢美少女做女友。<br />\n貪心的是不只要一個，最好多四個。<br />\n<br />\n而我要求唔多，有左手和右手就夠。<br />\n可能我不是男人，是男仔吧。<br />\n<br />\n大人的世界真深奧...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5472b29333e3c8e063cb9119d51c074635c3575","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:34:15.000Z","msg":"還是進不了黑洞...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解，點解連admin都唔鐘意我。<br />\n<br />\nbtw，我也不想做第三者。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3822973e86deaf2dbac035f1bbe5b3bbc3347b98","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:35:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會繼續上次個故<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我本來就唔識寫文，詞語貧窮。<br />\n還有，我唔識中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重諗住有痴線故事睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你會睇依個post已夠癡線，唔駛睇故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9000a251c16eb8e95896385076f964a98b24d2e4","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:37:15.000Z","msg":"依個世界有兩種人，一種是有撚用，另一種是無撚用。<br />\n癡線佬是有撚用中帶點無撚用。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca1a1b7035b37c0202429049840f8e92b9a450f","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"愛不是說出口，而是做出來。<br />\n但做得要小心點，如果唔係因大得小。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565ab6bfca64f697e6794eaceade5dbeaa3b141d","tid":39362,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:40:57.000Z","msg":"哈囉癡線佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感謝你一直向admin爭取癡線佬台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係癡線架"},{"pid":"4c8eee04e041b3d2a17d66d331e55ea85c964100","tid":39362,"uid":23661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:41:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我本來就唔識寫文，詞語貧窮。<br />\n還有，我唔識中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重諗住有痴線故事睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你會睇依個post已夠癡線，唔駛睇故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我又好記認真睇哂呢個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係咪開始痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6cb7560b6d3caf7ea7c3225d3d0d76ea99b6a1","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:42:15.000Z","msg":"飲淡水先，寫到口乾。"},{"pid":"c7a7a3eb63514bade88b7caffe0522fff9dbe9ea","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:43:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哈囉癡線佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感謝你一直向admin爭取癡線佬台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係癡線架</blockquote><br />\n你唔係癡線，也要記得食藥，乖啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791ba26729b8ac05e090edc0989615e75f839520","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:44:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我本來就唔識寫文，詞語貧窮。<br />\n還有，我唔識中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重諗住有痴線故事睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你會睇依個post已夠癡線，唔駛睇故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我又好記認真睇哂呢個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係咪開始痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴線不是那麼簡單，你只係癡鳩線，打個jj就冇事，放心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d1c846d735f5aebe435375ed34eeb3fa1a6dd0","tid":39362,"uid":23661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:46:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你會睇依個post已夠癡線，唔駛睇故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我又好記認真睇哂呢個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係咪開始痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴線不是那麼簡單，你只係癡鳩線，打個jj就冇事，放心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點樣先可以做到你個境界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e01836074319799b52bbc0a56311212072d65ec","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:47:10.000Z","msg":"個個人也是苦幹為生活。<br />\n在我眼裡只是個個人也為生存。<br />\n<br />\n壓力使人生活不了，做做癡線佬為生存又何防呢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e86b8cf9d1670f25eabdcbbed80965eb7b573e3","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:50:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你會睇依個post已夠癡線，唔駛睇故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我又好記認真睇哂呢個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係咪開始痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴線不是那麼簡單，你只係癡鳩線，打個jj就冇事，放心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點樣先可以做到你個境界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇多點av就可以了，兩用反手打個靚j，4杯精煮成8杯精，之後抹身，再叫你呀媽打鳩你，就有5.28%機會成癡線佬，唔好教人呀，秘密來的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfdf2a939f396100b2fcd6cf00fd0791a017b8b2","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:52:02.000Z","msg":"還有4分22秒，還是入唔到黑洞，可能我要返去我呀媽個黑洞了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a647b06925b8dd136a4512b7324910e04c684ba2","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:52:50.000Z","msg":"天生我材必無用，小事難成變成瘋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3515ed8ad55b2708da431bfe0855f92b4190be","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:54:20.000Z","msg":"可能有一日，我不會癡線了。<br />\n不是我長大了，而是我唔識扯旗了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49924a40718943efe4be3f7a017143abee9d12e0","tid":39362,"uid":32973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:54:41.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7db146fbb747c3d0bac26dc8a5a4380294fa84","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:56:10.000Z","msg":"還有52秒，多謝幾位觀眾。<br />\n叫咗你地唔好入來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後我想就一句:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAdmin幾時開個癡線佬台比我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1373297fb9caf9aba7cce2ee9f2a292fe7b0202","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:56:56.000Z","msg":"完，最後還是入唔到黑洞，FUCK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8017351e14fea21b2393a944f76e496061e43c","tid":39362,"uid":11194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:00:56.000Z","msg":"其實黑洞係咩黎"},{"pid":"1b3cb4e8d0b30f7bedad74e237e1502707161609","tid":39362,"uid":23661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:05:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完，最後還是入唔到黑洞，FUCK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為你十連唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc69df8aa05559dd70143cdd02189043eb2a57f","tid":39362,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>哈囉癡線佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感謝你一直向admin爭取癡線佬台</blockquote><br />\n你唔係癡線，也要記得食藥，乖啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食咗啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食咗Admin就會開癡線佬台架啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你要唔要食一甩啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ead8ebc53a71bdfb5e516d1b08e6c24ebb2cbc","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:12:43.000Z","msg":"諗諗下，這個post幾好，得閒會在這個post發一發下癡線故。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a417748e96ec313705d6f1a7f02b201273fe6b","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:14:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實黑洞係咩黎</blockquote><br />\n黑洞是外星生物的地頭，那裡無人理人，想屌就屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e51469d1c458b638b41935cab0f4fae21cb9df5","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>哈囉癡線佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感謝你一直向admin爭取癡線佬台</blockquote><br />\n你唔係癡線，也要記得食藥，乖啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食咗啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食咗Admin就會開癡線佬台架啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你要唔要食一甩啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食咗柯but luck，有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c2aabba054fe977a0253716a7e24c06a44dcf5","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:23:51.000Z","msg":"發多一個post就訓。<br />\n<br />\n五月三十二日  睛<br />\n在7時50分34秒的早上，一個英俊又有點瘋狂的癡線佬起床。<br />\n他有床上沉思，夠竟世上有雞先定有老媽子先呢。<br />\n他，想不透。可能要問問雞蛋。<br />\n<br />\n最後，用念力打個飛機後就起床。<br />\n<br />\n去了大廳，見到你女友一號ipad坐係度。<br />\n然後佢同ipad講:<br />\n<br />\n今日你還是那麼平，真叫人慾仙慾死。<br />\n<br />\n1小時5分後，他出門返學...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個故下次繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0afbcf2852d35e1806543cad4cbdd126738ae7c5","tid":39362,"uid":23661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9fcc3ba3800a97f69691c7871c44a7c626c4df0","tid":39362,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n食咗柯but luck，有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c79d889473d9075783d485ed0a0f2dda76ee93e","tid":39362,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重有冇文出"},{"pid":"c1a313c15f8f1c1a65ae4e4d1b0a359544ca44e8","tid":39362,"uid":23661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重有冇文出</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都等緊文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2983d3fed38f234473067fb313313a679203cae6","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:05:40.000Z","msg":"返學途上，還是做我的最愛，一邊唱歌一邊跳學心舞。<br />\n<br />\nonon99  onon9  9onon9  9onon9<br />\n(如果閣下知道依首係乜野歌，恭喜你，你有絕對音感和年紀有咁上吓)<br />\n<br />\n返到學校，見到賭撚，當然賭兩手啦。<br />\n今日賭的是鳩毛，和他吹下水抆下鳩毛，佢同我講：<br />\n<br />\n昨晚同廠長賭撚賭到輸咗條撚，但同時八到一個傳說，傳說話如果可以集齊所有admin入同一個post，仲要佢地一同屌鳩你，神龍會賜比佢一個願望。<br />\n<br />\n！！！真唔真呀！！！最後同賭撚賭完贏咗佢千幾條鳩毛，夠鐘上牛河博士堂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce956d1c290c17482420a30f5d6027290c7d764","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:06:39.000Z","msg":"在10時15分34秒，我去到牛河博士教室。我校分了好多學科，如<br />\n手機科、體育科、動漫科、感情科、吹水科等等，要乜科有乜科。<br />\n唯一無的科是癡線佬科，所以我現在上的只是癡線佬偽員訓練班，但我相信，總有一日癡線佬會自成一科的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1c8e5f94f0e5f8f263114c5c163e7b505b4733","tid":39362,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:07:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a3cf4b90bc38250ce55eba7e8072272bdf011d2","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:08:20.000Z","msg":"今日牛河博士教的是如何用念力分別癡線、癡鳩線和癡撚線。<br />\n原來，真係有分別。大致上是：<br />\n鳩者硬也，其性衝動，宜屌不宜射。<br />\n撚者柒也，其性軟弱，宜揸不宜插。<br />\n癡線者，無鳩可用，無撚柒用，取之中庸，用之中庸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82dd88ff7b024e96cd1e61ca56d8a4e041fa4188","tid":39362,"uid":21871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae786d86d84a771f8f8eb04b4baec4db387db1ea","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:12:17.000Z","msg":"下課後，由於不停諗今日賭撚講嘅傳說，唔小心行樓梯踏空了。<br />\n幸好身手不凡，用空中轉體312度再後空翻799度順手除埋條褲落地。<br />\n雖然人沒受傷，但斷咗小小腳毛。所以去了醫務室見關醫生。<br />\n關醫生話傷情嚴重，要用白汁煮紅毛泥封西湯比我搽身。<br />\n但她又講現在手上無紅毛泥，淨係得個西，問我要唔要。<br />\n仲話白汁要我出&hellip;<br />\n佢都癡線，我一口回絕，頭也不回返屋企邊打jj邊計劃如何令傳說成真。<br />\n但我發現一個致命問題...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在是五月三十二日晚上9時10分46秒，個lihkg討論區都未開，我點實行我大計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998b457ebb568ed4dbecc17f704a06156c62d452","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:13:14.000Z","msg":"個故下次繼續，今日忙，多謝收看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239ffac5135651dbd7c9c90b36ba7711c05427f0","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:22:28.000Z","msg":"原來寫文是一件好難的事，加上我有閱寫腦閉塞症。<br />\n真係相當敬佩所有講故佬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e40a2f0ac786b0aad306f75cf802c46bf894052","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:24:38.000Z","msg":"還有之前落海故是有結局的，請用起底模式看最後幾頁，多請合作。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e923696ba8c295404187537e3527614019665a","tid":39362,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T03:30:12.000Z","msg":"寂寞在流動 某些真的假的夢"},{"pid":"fcb9539660eac7d813f3a77e165369b9dcf6a28e","tid":39362,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想快啲有癡線佬台"},{"pid":"89d66109e3ba0737479ae43e9b019bfe2dbe7aff","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:32:02.000Z","msg":"現在有時間，快快手手完左個故仔佢。<br />\n我喜歡爛尾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d4901290206635863f2132893ed08ac275f46f","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:34:01.000Z","msg":"十二月九日 淫中帶賤雨不停<br />\n<br />\n時光飛逝，五月到十二月發生了很多事，如：<br />\n<br />\n-我掉了前女友落海。<br />\n-我女友係三上悠亞之妹大戰機械獸。<br />\n-在日本連住尼尋找連尼住時連住尼不見連尼住西人事件薄。<br />\n-比卡超相約小火龍如何掉奇異種子入樹海捉卡比獸。<br />\n等等&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n發生太多，不能盡錄，但我也由癡撚線進化成癡鳩線再加上吞咗mega石，變成一個終極癡線佬。<br />\n<br />\nAR... pi...pi...pi你老母<br />\n仆街MON 日夜鍛鍊去屌西<br />\n沿路看遍每個癡線　屌過豆腐插爆火山<br />\nI LOVE仆街MON　認定你是癡線佬<br />\n屌開西窿的愛　便能用盡力量 <br />\nFUCK<br />\n<br />\n所以，我要爆了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f038ae7be8d6e61dd6134752c5deab0b7efa18","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:37:46.000Z","msg":"十二月十日 萬千西山屌不停<br />\n<br />\n終於等到lihkg開門了，但高調如我也會怕羞，所以遲遲不敢開account。<br />\n自問自己癡線力不足，只有食6包營多增加多點性能力。<br />\n<br />\n最後開了一個account叫火宅，如果你問我有何意思，我會答你：<br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔撚知，求其在家裡隨手拿一本日歷其中一頁選兩個字。<br />\n<br />\n在十二月十日2時1分40秒，我發了第一個post<br />\n&ldquo;Admin可唔可以開一個癡線佬台比我&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n結果大家都知，失敗，可能我唔夠癡線，太有禮貌。<br />\nAdmin依啲正常人唔會理我。<br />\n我對著天空高叫點解，點解無人明白一個癡線佬也會有性需要。<br />\n但記得三上悠亞同我講過：<br />\n<br />\n同情自己只有on9仔會做的事。<br />\n<br />\n多謝你三上悠亞，我曾經的愛。<br />\n最後反手打了兩個靚j去訓覺，其中一個是獻給三上悠亞。<br />\nbtw，閣位打完飛機記得洗手，如果唔係會生蟲的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7615a27c1df076c7506ac3a540b6f006e1c0b0b","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"十二月十二日 飛雪連天倚賓州<br />\n<br />\n昨日，和賭撚研究如何令admin們入我post屌鳩我。佢講：<br />\n<br />\n直播除褲啦，莊重得來又帶點專重，on9得來又帶點童真，今時今日賭撚唔值錢架啦，萬般皆無品，唯有除褲高。<br />\n<br />\n我聽完佢咁講，立刻三省吾身，碌鳩抽筋。<br />\n點解我諗唔到呢，所以決定明日直播除褲，希望能得admin注意。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56da0512250eb656f62f7fcd869b98b95961ea3","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:43:25.000Z","msg":"十二月十三日  笑書俠神掉落海<br />\n<br />\n本來要開除褲post，但碌鳩兩頭fing，連我都企唔定。<br />\n見我碌鳩唔想出鏡，加上怕被ban，又怕人話我5p、狗公。<br />\n所以出賣回憶，開了個post：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;女友問我你呀媽同我掉落海你會救邊個&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n估唔到，咁多人笑，反應又幾好，但我唔明白，<br />\n明明是一段可歌可泣淡淡悲哀的愛情故事，點解會變成笑話&hellip;<br />\n我看不透，可能癡線佬不能理解正常人的思考，人與人的關係真遙遠&hellip;<br />\nbtw，最後admin還是沒進來&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d591089a0bff5d8dd40f35803f9649f05e88f1","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:44:24.000Z","msg":"本故事完，多請收看爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8cc1bf3ba862ac3026c3ca549ea08fbc0a81e7","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:44:56.000Z","msg":"後記<br />\n<br />\n人生太多遺憾的事，就算唔成功，我也曾努力過。最後送上這歌給閣位：<br />\n<br />\n無盡<br />\n夢想於漆黑裡仍然鏗鏘仍然大聲高唱仍然期待世界給我鼓掌<br />\n是妄想趁現在追趕失散方向<br />\n曾懷著心底的信仰千次萬次跌傷<br />\n開始不敢回頭尋覓那真相明日那個幻想<br />\n也開始不甘被雕刻成石像<br />\n<br />\n踏上這無盡旅途過去飄散消散失散花火<br />\n重燃起重燃點起鼓舞 <br />\n或許到最後沒有完美句號<br />\n仍然倔強冒險一一去征討<br />\n踏上這無盡旅途誰又能鑑定你的醜惡與美好<br />\n<br />\n低與高離隊抹走那刺心挖苦的勸告<br />\n人生夢一場革命至蒼老<br />\n<br />\n夢想存活在別人期待那獎賞<br />\n最後連自己都相信勇氣不再熱血結霜<br />\n開始裹足停留開始習慣體諒<br />\n也開始不甘被倒模的一個用剩餘力氣去吧鼓掌<br />\n<br />\n太多太多構思踫壁<br />\n太多太多理想壓抑<br />\n沉默對應著歲月無聲<br />\n天空尚有片夕陽帶領<br />\n<br />\n踏上這無盡旅途過去飄散消散失散花火<br />\n重燃起重燃點起鼓舞 <br />\n或許到最後沒有完美句號<br />\n仍然倔強冒險一一去征討<br />\n踏上這無盡旅途誰又能鑑定你的醜惡與美好<br />\n來提步壯闊跑道<br />\n合十雙手去禱告<br />\n<br />\n人生夢一場革命至蒼老<br />\n難得夢一場革命不老"},{"pid":"33f554d1bd3ab07e220d346395612fcdb2418d76","tid":39362,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:45:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本故事完，多請收看爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n結果依然冇癡線佬台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817e720b514b4cc15b830978b8bd8c4ab3476612","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:45:34.000Z","msg":"生活迫人，<br />\n可能你忘記了如何歡笑，<br />\n可能你得不到你要的結果。<br />\n如果你壓力大到喘不過氣，<br />\n歡迎你進入癡線佬的世界。<br />\n就算係扮，記得扮完後出返去現實繼續努力，加油。還有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAdmin幾時問個癡線佬台比我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af084f4fa3c70f2cfcb9b9b6ccdf803f2349590","tid":39362,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:46:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生活迫人，<br />\n可能你忘記了如何歡笑，<br />\n可能你得不到你要的結果。<br />\n如果你壓力大到喘不過氣，<br />\n歡迎你進入癡線佬的世界。<br />\n就算係扮，記得扮完後出返去現實繼續努力，加油。還有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAdmin幾時問個癡線佬台比我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快啲開啊"},{"pid":"23ac3f36dd46972faf4d04c748a4213d73bed2f3","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d5e013e79aa43f6ceceb98e612cefb4b46d681","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:55:58.000Z","msg":"依五日打嘅中文字等如我10年零58日打字總和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824cff36e1f