-12-16T12:09:49.000Z","msg":"個po做乜鳩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68763d0c2f2a6d9bc4f39df6c117d712ac0bc0f","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T12:27:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個po做乜鳩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恭喜你，進入咗癡線佬的思考領域。<br />\n個post係專門比我得閒入來打飛機用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc174a4d8b3142f7553a50b75407422064c763d","tid":39362,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:24:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個po做乜鳩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恭喜你，進入咗癡線佬的思考領域。<br />\n個post係專門比我得閒入來打飛機用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我是來睇文的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0238c0fa2c84d8597250bcb7579dbe42f59de7","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:35:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個po做乜鳩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恭喜你，進入咗癡線佬的思考領域。<br />\n個post係專門比我得閒入來打飛機用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我是來睇文的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁俾面，我立刻寫多篇極速短文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d40aa85bb1ffc855bf97c52227b668b22535fc8","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:37:29.000Z","msg":"女孩對男孩說:<br />\n唔好成日扮低b仔令我笑，如果有一日我唔喺你身邊，你也要成日笑呀，我最鐘意你笑。<br />\n<br />\n男孩沒有回答女孩，反而扮傻，說:<br />\n願我王仙褔永享，壽與天齊。<br />\n<br />\n在三十二天16時34分後，女孩已經不見了。<br />\n<br />\n男孩在家裡看著與女孩有關的一切物件，面帶微笑說:<br />\n謝謝你，和妳的曾經，是我一生的運氣。<br />\n如果再有機會再見你，就算是夢中也好，我還是會扮低b仔引你笑，因為我也最鐘意你笑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"92a46b3db889fa284ffef63075aeeaea53e9c003","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:59:41.000Z","msg":"你將來想做什麼，依句野我成日比人問，難道我天生真係一副唔知做乜撚嘢嘅樣？<br />\n<br />\n細個時，老師問我:<br />\n你將來想做什麼呀？火宅。<br />\n<br />\n我答:<br />\n食飯、訓覺、打jj<br />\n<br />\n最後老師話我犯咗淫褻與不雅，罰我抄&rdquo;我以後不打jj&quot;一千次。<br />\n其實我唔明我有多淫褻與不雅&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebf27efdc0a0cbbc7809591718e63dbececb7a2","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:00:39.000Z","msg":"畢業後，有日在家裡呀媽問我:<br />\n你將來想做什麼呀？火宅。<br />\n<br />\n我答:<br />\n食飯、訓覺、打jj<br />\n<br />\n最後呀媽同我講，呀仔，打少啲jj呀，傷身呀。<br />\n其實我唔明打jj有幾傷身...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53bf76a55e8f2c25c5a1d4797e2116cdd585a72b","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:02:45.000Z","msg":"打工時，老闆問我:<br />\n你將來想做什麼呀？火宅。(我都唔明啲老闆咁鐘意問人依條問題&hellip;)<br />\n<br />\n我答:<br />\n食飯、訓覺、打jj<br />\n<br />\n最後老闆話公司不准員工不純潔的交往，<br />\n一係就要份工，一係就要條j，我最後選擇咗我條j。<br />\n其實我唔明打j有幾咁不純潔...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5679ed6360ffd42798afb8e77ef6246d270b77","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:04:17.000Z","msg":"拍拖時，女友問我:<br />\n你將來想做什麼呀？火宅。<br />\n<br />\n我答:<br />\n食飯、訓覺、打jj<br />\n<br />\n最後女友話佢自己已經滿足唔不我，<br />\n情願打jj都唔搞佢，而又覺得我唔夠愛佢，分手了&hellip;<br />\n其實我唔明打j同愛有乜關係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58498ad16efcfa4c12d9b0c5c48cca700dba8d3e","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"我真係唔明，難道我打jj係罪大滔天？世間無人可以容納我條撚？<br />\n所以，到我低頭問我條撚:<br />\n細佬呀，細佬，你將來想做什麼呀？<br />\n<br />\n好神奇，我同條撚好似心靈相通咁，佢仲用心聲來回答我：<br />\n<br />\n(一把老牛聲) 細佬答: 屌你，成日打我，仲要打到我口吐白沫，<br />\n我情願比其他人打，我都唔想比你打死！！！<br />\n<br />\n最後我當我自己幻聽，每日如常食飯、訓覺、打jj。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"956a5aed053a88e9312682ecc7a51e786b020e77","tid":39362,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:47:08.000Z","msg":"助樓主入黑洞"},{"pid":"fd600d44c448bbd01d2c3455acb79bcc6186fb10","tid":39362,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:47:20.000Z","msg":"1."},{"pid":"371b35e3fa1abe36ecbf7fe1c5c015aa4846378b","tid":39362,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:47:30.000Z","msg":"2.."},{"pid":"ad7ec432a297dd58b7d1dc5bebd71f7aab94b659","tid":39362,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:47:40.000Z","msg":"3...."},{"pid":"39ca2ba5bc8e933bb4da5b1c2a96b7e3bcb7de5f","tid":39362,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:48:00.000Z","msg":"似乎連巴有機制對付十連"},{"pid":"d4f478223e566aaf6aacf0633a06a92ba9ce6afd","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:00:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似乎連巴有機制對付十連</blockquote><br />\n連黑洞都唔收我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea2809f62c49c7aa93ffa67ee8c16e5170b629c","tid":39362,"uid":57780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:05:25.000Z","msg":"一鍵留明睇癡線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff22e27fd8b34a82ab370038b29397266f05891e","tid":39362,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女孩對男孩說:<br />\n唔好成日扮低b仔令我笑，如果有一日我唔喺你身邊，你也要成日笑呀，我最鐘意你笑。<br />\n<br />\n男孩沒有回答女孩，反而扮傻，說:<br />\n願我王仙褔永享，壽與天齊。<br />\n<br />\n在三十二天16時34分後，女孩已經不見了。<br />\n<br />\n男孩在家裡看著與女孩有關的一切物件，面帶微笑說:<br />\n謝謝你，和妳的曾經，是我一生的運氣。<br />\n如果再有機會再見你，就算是夢中也好，我還是會扮低b仔引你笑，因為我也最鐘意你笑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似睇其他癡線佬文睇過類似<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係咪已經冇得救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8098a8b8839ae3465e79e8cd046a55d52a687dd7","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:16:51.000Z","msg":"每個人心中也有個癡線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24022a90dfdafa96daee73e440002b73bb1ead1d","tid":39362,"uid":49275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"巴打你文采又唔算差點解變左癡線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 支持癡線台"},{"pid":"2e4a3726d4ef25e33d0906ac1b4eb80df384a55b","tid":39362,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 温final温到癡咗線"},{"pid":"7f343818be2874f32930b10560cfc72178243f79","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你文采又唔算差點解變左癡線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 支持癡線台</blockquote><br />\n依家癡線佬好失禮你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認真答你，上得lihkg多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f50a42a014b02c9d7d8adf2862b87561e1c42c9","tid":39362,"uid":44982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:20:43.000Z","msg":"好比火星跟水星相戀有過燦爛影踪"},{"pid":"92ae561b43f373428a99d47c00b193882caac625","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"如果有生日期<br />\n等多一百歲亦等待妳<br />\n未曾害怕這天與地淪為晒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4f9e73bd759be5e2c6243b247316476a7e48e7","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:25:36.000Z","msg":"當你地覺得累了，不愉快了。<br />\n入來這post，打個飛機，之後出返去。<br />\n又一條好漢。<br />\n<br />\nbtw，打完飛機記得洗手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe112359a7ef35319b40bdc650556d61c108408","tid":39362,"uid":23661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:47:22.000Z","msg":"隔咗成日一入呢個post 見到有文睇 好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e034596a89cef473c44f10f7f1873457280be3","tid":39362,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T01:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有文啊 推下先"},{"pid":"b407946db6ed30cc196f810c1e6cbd7ba5510c22","tid":39362,"uid":19892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T01:19:13.000Z","msg":"因為你去探索黑洞唔預我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0adb817f9f5eda8218bda4ef560aef0bbab6ed45","tid":39362,"uid":42146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T01:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴線佬"},{"pid":"9af0e0cae127ec466992110b52a6efaff0253f30","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為你去探索黑洞唔預我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n癡線佬係孤傲的生物，只能一個人踏上無盡的黑洞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61bd5ec46138108dc16393f491e14872b61e8be5","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"有日，我和我的大姐吵架，她說：<br />\n你知唔知我係你救命恩人，如果唔係我，你早就死咗啦。<br />\n<br />\n我大惑不解，我大姐幾撚時有救過我，連我自己都唔知，所以反駁說:<br />\n你唔好吹得就吹，思覺失調就去飲司各脫啦。<br />\n<br />\n大姐激動地說：<br />\n你個仆街仔，當年唔係我靜雞雞去呀爸呀媽間房用針拮穿晒佢地啲避孕套，你早就和你啲兄弟一齊戰死西場！！！<br />\n<br />\n我恍然大悟，難怪我細細個就覺得自己比其他人癡線，原來我大姐拮穿個洞口太細，搞到我撞親個頭...<br />\n<br />\n最後我流著淚對我大姐說：<br />\n大姐，如果你再想要個細佬妹，記得用大頭針拮穿呀爸呀媽啲避孕套...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274c361c8d3c66ac68e0228cb5092cda23f0189a","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:36:05.000Z","msg":"矛盾只因鳩痛著，你知嗎。<br />\n誰期望這刻抽插完，然後抖吓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52be1d9e9cf1ecfa9a6c6bb34ae9c0a39842b2c0","tid":39362,"uid":23661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:45:24.000Z","msg":"#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"6fe38df4b516adc2de5b481a95b6365fa2e91ae3","tid":39362,"uid":60128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:55:08.000Z","msg":"依排唔得閒，唔會更新。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}